        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1896919781" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6179111907398346681">Jemima Puddle-Duck is a very stupid duck (in the author&apos;s words) and gets herself into quite a pickle. Fortunately a friend dog sees the problem and does something about it. Beautifully illustrated and written.</span>
  <span id="freeText6179111907398346681" style="display:none">Jemima Puddle-Duck is a very stupid duck (in the author's words) and gets herself into quite a pickle. Fortunately a friend dog sees the problem and does something about it. Beautifully illustrated and written.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6179111907398346681" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
